### Variables (ajusta host/puertos si corres sin Docker)
@menuHost = http://localhost:3001
@orderHost = http://localhost:3002
@notificationHost = http://localhost:3003

### Health checks
GET {{menuHost}}/health
GET {{orderHost}}/health
GET {{notificationHost}}/health

### Menú
GET {{menuHost}}/menu
GET {{menuHost}}/menu/combo-campero

### Crear pedido (valida contra menú y publica order.created)
POST {{orderHost}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "María Pérez",
  "items": [
    { "productId": "combo-campero", "quantity": 1 },
    { "productId": "papas-mediana", "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### Listar pedidos (lectura vía READ_DB_URL / réplica simulada)
GET {{orderHost}}/orders

### Pedido por id (sustituye UUID)
GET {{orderHost}}/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Actualizar estado (publica order.updated)
PATCH {{orderHost}}/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed"
}
